title: Hour 3 - Michigan Melee Mystery, Jim Nantz
itunes:title: Hour 3 - Michigan Melee Mystery, Jim Nantz
description:
Dan gets firsthand details from Michigan State insider Kyle Austin who was in the tunnel and witnessed the fisticuffs that erupted after the Michigan State-Michigan game. And he talks to broadcasting legend Jim Nantz as he enters the twilight of his career.

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
